{
  "stem": "2684.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And then he unbuttoned my fly and started playing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And while he was playing with us-- he was-- with me, actually-- he started asking questions, whether my parents had been in the resistance movement, or, or do we have anything to hide, like papers or, or valuables or whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And while he was asking the question, he was playing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And I knew what he was doing, because, as I said, I'd been grown up in the street.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And I knowed that he's a homosexual.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "But I never had encounter, actually, in my time, which is very different way of thinking.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "We made fun of homosexuals if we knew, because on the market, it was toilets.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And on the toilets in the evening, these people are gathered.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "But those days, was against the law, so they were very low profile.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I couldn't tell him anything about my parents, because I never knew that my parents had anything to do with, with any organization which was resistance, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know anything about our wealth, because we'd never been informed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My parents never told me what we have, what we haven't got.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when this finished, I went out, and the next guy came in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as children, we were absolutely mesmerized, what happened to us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I might be-- I might been very young, but, thanks God, that was my first and last experience of that kind.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That it, it didn't leave a mark on me, but I, I remember it like-- I remember the face of the bastard.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when the-- all the interrogation was over, they put us on a truck.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the truck went down to the side of the Danube, what we called the, the rock part.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
